revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
This template is like [[mw:Help:Extension:ParserFunctions##ifeq|#ifeq]], but does not [[m:Help:Newlines_and_spaces#Trimming_on_expansion|trim]] the "then" and "else" part.
=== Usage ===
*<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" inline>{{ifeq|"abc"|"abc"| 1 | 0 }}</syntaxhighlight> gives "{{ifeq|"abc"|"abc"| 1 | 0 }}"
*<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" inline>{{ifeq|"abc"|"def"| 1 | 0 }}</syntaxhighlight> gives "{{ifeq|"abc"|"def"| 1 | 0 }}"
*<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" inline>{{ifeq|{{PAGENAME}}|Ifeq| 1 | 0 }}</syntaxhighlight> gives "{{ifeq|{{PAGENAME}}|Ifeq| 1 | 0 }}"

=== See also ===
*{{tl|If}}
*[[m:Template:Ifeq]]

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
[[Category:Parameter selection templates]]
}}</includeonly>

